Definition: A description of the conditions or context of an observation, for example, under sedation, fasting or post-exercise. A qualifier cannot modify the measurement type; for example, a fasting blood sugar is still a blood sugar.

Short: Code representing a description of the conditions or context of an observation, for example, under sedation, fasting or post-exercise. A qualifier cannot modify the measurement type; for example, a fasting blood sugar is still a blood sugar.
